            <h2>What Are AI Agents?</h2>
            <p>AI agents are autonomous software programs designed to perform specific tasks, make decisions, and learn from interactions. Unlike traditional automation, these agents can adapt to new situations, understand context, and provide personalized responses.</p>

            <h3>Key Characteristics of Modern AI Agents:</h3>
