              <li><strong>Pilot Program:</strong> Begin with a limited deployment to test and refine</li>
              <li><strong>Training and Integration:</strong> Ensure seamless integration with existing systems</li>
              <li><strong>Continuous Optimization:</strong> Regular monitoring and improvement cycles</li>
            </ol>

